    "content": "nullLoyalty Management\nTABLE OF CONTENTS\nClose\nClose\nSearch\nSearch\n Loyalty Management\n Get Started with Loyalty Management\n Control Who Sees What in Loyalty Management\n Loyalty Program Setup Basics\n Create a Loyalty Program\n Loyalty Tier Groups\n Loyalty Tiers\n Loyalty Program Currencies\n Loyalty Program Members\n Create a Loyalty Program Member\n Member Groups\n Member Engagement Attributes\n Member Badges\n Member Badge Workflow\n Create Loyalty Program Badges\n Assign Badges to Members\n Member Referral Code\n Manage Loyalty Program Partners\n Manage and Work with Benefits\n Manage and Work with Vouchers\n Manage and Work with Promotions\n Offer Games to Members\n Integrate Loyalty Management with External Systems\n Settings for Loyalty Processes\n Set Up Loyalty Processes\n Create Loyalty Program Processes by Using Promotion Setup\n Member Engagement Widgets\n Mobile SDK for Loyalty Management\n Manage Loyalty Program Members\n Loyalty Service Excellence\n Manage and View Transaction Journals\n Set Up Experiences for Loyalty Program Members\n Get a Head Start on Your Day with the Home Page\n Integrate Loyalty Management with Marketing Cloud\n Integrate Loyalty Management with Service Cloud\n Supported Loyalty Management Objects for Shield Platform Encryption\n Create a Loyalty Management Trial Org\n Loyalty Analytics Base App\n Deploy and Use Analytics for Loyalty\n Loyalty Management on Hyperforce\n Languages Supported by Loyalty Management\n Data Deletion for Loyalty Management\n Data Access and Export for Loyalty Management\n Restrict Data Processing for Loyalty Management\n Consent Management for Loyalty Management\n Data Archive for Loyalty Management\n\nYou are here:\n\nSALESFORCE HELP\nDOCS\nLOYALTY MANAGEMENT\nMember Badges\n\nAssign badges to members based on members’ interaction with your loyalty program. You can assign badges to recognize member milestones or other specific activities.\n\nREQUIRED EDITIONS\nAvailable in: Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Developer, and Unlimited Editions\nAvailable in: Orgs that have the B2C - Loyalty, B2C - Loyalty Plus, B2B - Loyalty, Loyalty Management - Growth, or Loyalty Management - Advanced license enabled\nExplore and Learn\n\nWatch this video to understand how to add rewards for your loyalty program.\n\nIf you aren’t able to watch the video in full screen, open the video on a new tab:  Add a Loyalty Program’s Rewards.\n\nMember Badge Workflow\nBefore you start creating badges for your loyalty program and assigning the badges to members, learn the complete workflow to create, assign, and track member badges.\nCreate Loyalty Program Badges\nCreate Loyalty Program Badge records to define badges to assign to members based on your company’s requirements. For example, you can create badges for each of the tiers in your loyalty program or to recognize the top contributors on the program’s community.\nAssign Badges to Members\nUse actions in loyalty program process rules to assign badges to members and to check whether a badge is assigned to a member.\nDID THIS ARTICLE SOLVE YOUR ISSUE?\nLet us know so we can improve!\nYes\nNo\n ",
